"FEATURES:

Wargame: Red Dragon - the first edition of the popular series of strategies in real time, which takes place outside of Europe: this time-scale military conflict is unfolding in Asia between 1975 and 1991. The game features 17 countries, including five new ones, including China and North Korea. Arsenal added more than 450 kinds of troops and military equipment - their total number now exceeds 1,300. Specifically, Wargame: Red Dragon appeared naval forces and amphibious ATVs, as well as maps with water for their use, that opens up a host of new strategic features.

Fans of single player game Wargame: Red Dragon offer campaign on the bloody conflict that erupted around Korea, and those who prefer the multiplayer battles, - the time-tested multiplayer mode with support for up to 20 participants.
